00:17:25,190 --> 00:17:27,260
<font size="40">Who will be called first?</font>

308
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:28,730
<font size="40">Ikuta Erika</font>

309
00:17:28,730 --> 00:17:35,870
<font size="40">Her unwavering spirit continues to leave a strong impact, Ikuta,</font>

