00:17:35,870 --> 00:17:37,940
<font size="40">she's in the first row this time.</font>

311
00:17:38,470 --> 00:17:41,570
<font size="40">After hearing everyone’s stories,</font>

312
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:44,910
